OL,3,CLabour to look into law supporting
OL,4,Cparents of critically ill children
OL,6,FIt would give parents the right to
OL,7,Fstatutory paid leave and job
OL,8,Fprotection from day one for parents
OL,9,Fwhose child is diagnosed with a
OL,10,Fcritical or terminal illness, up to
OL,11,Fthe age of 16.
OL,13,FCeri and Frances said a consultation
OL,14,Falone is "not enough" and that it must
OL,15,Fdeliver real change. They are calling
OL,16,Ffor paid leave and job protection for
OL,17,Fparents when their child is critically
OL,18,Fill.
