OL,3,CLabour to look into law supporting
OL,4,Cparents of critically ill children
OL,6,F"This is progress that we welcome and
OL,7,Fis the culmination of three years hard
OL,8,Fwork, but it is far from over and far
OL,9,Ffrom won", the parents added.
OL,11,F"Ten families face this reality every
OL,12,Fsingle day, and they still have no
OL,13,Flegal right to be by their child's
OL,14,Fside. We will not stop until Hugh's
OL,15,FLaw is in place and parents get the
OL,16,Fdignity and support they deserve."
