OL,6,FBut the government has told ITV News
OL,7,Fit will look into their proposals in
OL,8,Fthe new year.
OL,10,FA spokesperson said: "We recognise
OL,11,Fthat serious childhood illness
OL,12,Frepresents a challenging and stressful
OL,13,Ftime for families, which is why we
OL,14,Fhave committed to a public
OL,15,Fconsultation on support for parents
OL,16,Ffacing this situation.
