OL,3,CLabour to look into law supporting
OL,4,Cparents of critically ill children
OL,6,F"After he passed away, and during the
OL,7,Ftime that he had treatment, we
OL,8,Fwitnessed parents just going through
OL,9,Fthe worst time, obviously looking
OL,10,Fafter their child, but also the worst
OL,11,Ftime financially.
OL,13,F"And we realised at that point there
OL,14,Fis nothing in place in the UK that
OL,15,Fprovides support, financial support to
OL,16,Fparents of a sick child."
