OL,3,CLabour to look into law supporting
OL,4,Cparents of critically ill children
OL,6,FAt present, parents of critically ill
OL,7,Fchildren must rely on unpaid Carer's
OL,8,FLeave, which is capped at just one
OL,9,Fweek per year. Disability living
OL,10,Fallowance is available to claim on
OL,11,Fbehalf of the child, but parents must
OL,12,Fwait 90 days before applying and an
OL,13,Fapplication can take up to 20 weeks to
OL,14,Fbe processed.
