OL,7,Fcontinues. This is no longer a niche
OL,8,Fpolicy concern. It is becoming a
OL,9,Fmatter of public conscience. Families
OL,10,Fdeserve urgent action and Hugh's Law
OL,11,Fmust be addressed with the seriousness
OL,12,Fand speed this crisis demands."
